{"TopicId":132296,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Stupid rght click","CreatedByName":"DrDress","CreatedById":156575,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-17T00:57:13Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"DrDress","CreatedById":156575,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-17T00:57:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy right click button suddenly works badly. It\u0027s like it beeing held down or locked to certain parts. I have to click it repeatedly in order to get my curser back. It really annoying, especially at critical states in the mission. It started like a month or two ago. Any ideas what going on?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HebaruSan","CreatedById":156657,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-17T01:00:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDouble right click was added to lock mouse look in 1.0.5. I haven\u0027t seen a mod to remove this yet, but in the meantime, try not to double right click.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NathanKell","CreatedById":75006,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-17T01:15:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSettings-\u0026gt;Turn it off. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"katateochi","CreatedById":35181,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-17T02:03:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222413975\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132296\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455671715\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002275006\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022NathanKell\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n43 minutes ago, NathanKell said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSettings-\u0026gt;Turn it off. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you turn it off in settings you can still toggle it with \\ , (although I can\u0027t see a way to rebind that key, which is kinda odd, probably just an oversight)\u003Cbr\u003E\nso it\u0027s kinda best of both, as that mode is nice for cinematics but the accidental activation of it is\u00A0annoying.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FullMetalMachinist","CreatedById":156531,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-17T02:27:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222414047\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132296\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455674634\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002235181\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022katateochi\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n24 minutes ago, katateochi said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(although I can\u0027t see a way to rebind that key, which is kinda odd, probably just an oversight)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are quite a few keys that aren\u0027t available to edit in the settings menu in-game, but can be changed by manually editing the settings.cfg file. I believe this is one of them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-02-17T02:28:40Z\u0022 title=\u002202/17/2016 02:28  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 17, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by FullMetalMachinist\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-17T02:36:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222414047\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132296\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455674634\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002235181\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022katateochi\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n31 minutes ago, katateochi said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you turn it off in settings you can still toggle it with \\ , (although I can\u0027t see a way to rebind that key, which is kinda odd, probably just an oversight)\u003Cbr\u003E\nso it\u0027s kinda best of both, as that mode is nice for cinematics but the accidental activation of it is\u00A0annoying.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah. \u00A0I wish I could rebind the key to toggle zooming in/out, and going up and down (shift.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-17T06:25:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHuh.... Thought it was just me.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}